Going against the trend of metallic and shiny-plastic folder icons, I decided to try my hand at a more realistic material. After all, this is what most real folders look like.\
\
The thing that prompted me to do this was the realization that Apple's folder icon does not follow most of Apple's own icon design guidelines. Here are some quotes from the 
\f3\i Aqua Human Interface Guidelines
\f1\i0 :\
\
