\f1\i0 One thing that wasn't completely clear was the correct perspective for a folder icon. As far as other "file system object" icons go, disks use the angled top-down view, and files are straight-on. Neither one seemed to work well for folders, so I decided to match the angle used in application icons. The perspective didn't quite look good though, especially at smaller sizes, so I kept the rotation but reduced the perspective to just a couple of degrees.\
\
These icons have been carefully crafted to fit in with the other standard Aqua icons. If you can think of 
